<lyrics>[V1]
 Ngaituah nunnak thi sung bik cu, A luang lio atu ah, A kan Khamhtu thi
 tiva cu, Hawhra bantuk raannak, Hawhra bantuk raannak.

[C1]
   Hawhra bang raannak ah i kholh tuah u, A kholh duh vialte ahohmanh,
   An sual a thianter lai.

[V2]
 Kalvary tlang ah Khamhtu nih, Ngaihchiatnak kha a in; Amah thi sung a
 chuakmi kha, Hawhra bantuk raannak, Hawhra bantuk raannak.

[C2]
   Hawhra bang raannak ah i kholh tuah u, A kholh duh vialte ahohmanh,
   An sual a thianter lai.

[V3]
 Kan dihlak in kan kal kho lai, Tiva thi luannak ah, A thi sung bik kan
 zumh ahcun, Hawhra bang kan thiang lai, Hawhra bang kan thiang lai.

[C3]
   Hawhra bang raannak ah i kholh tuah u, A kholh duh vialte ahohmanh,
   An sual a thianter lai.

[V4]
 Bawi Jesuh a tum than tikah, A zummi a khawmh lai, A thi chuahnak a
 zummi lawng, Vancung khua an co lai, Vancung khua an co lai.

[C4]
   Hawhra bang raannak ah i kholh tuah u, A kholh duh vialte ahohmanh,
   An sual a thianter lai.</lyrics>
<title>NUNNAK THI SUNG CH135</title>
<hymn_number>135</hymn_number>
</song>